# Vision

This skill is a router. Root `VISION.md` is the mandatory doctrine entrypoint
and single project vision source.

## Rule

1. Read the active goal plan when one exists.
2. Read root `VISION.md`.
3. Read the owner skill/rule for execution details.
4. Put checkpoint evidence in the active plan, not in this skill.

Do not duplicate doctrine here. When reusable vision changes, edit root
`VISION.md`, then run `npx skiller@latest apply` so generated skills stay in
sync.
